OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry and clear with some patchy
OL,7,Ffrost. Clouding over from the south in
OL,8,Fthe early hours with a few showers
OL,9,Fspreading northeast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,12,Foccasional rain in the morning, this
OL,13,Fbecoming mostly confined to Argyll in
OL,14,Fthe evening. Chance of some clearer
OL,15,Fspells in the south later.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FCloudy with rain on Thursday, becoming
OL,19,Fdrier from the west later. Dry and
OL,20,Fbright on Friday and Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
